### 1. Level Order Traversal
# This uses the {{host}} variable from the environment file
POST {{protocol}}://{{host}}/api/v1/trees/level-order
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "value": 1,
  "left": {
    "value": 2,
    "left": { "value": 4 },
    "right": { "value": 5 }
  },
  "right": {
    "value": 3,
    "right": { "value": 6 }
  }
}

### 2. Health Check (Quarkus Default)
GET {{protocol}}://{{host}}/q/health
